  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK293">
<l>taṉṉeñ caṟivatu poyyaṟka poyttapiṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṉṉeñcē taṉṉaic cuṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let not a man knowingly tell a lie; for after he has told the lie, his mind will burn him (with the memory of his guilt).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
